Package: statquiz
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Statistics Practice in the R IDE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chayce", "Reed",
        email = "code.jcr@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for practicing statistics interactively inside
    your IDE. Generate randomized questions across eleven topics (ANOVA,
    t-tests, non-parametric tests, correlation, regression, probability,
    and more),
    solve them with standard R functions, and check your answers with
    immediate feedback. Includes a quiz mode for scored multi-question
    sessions and worked-solution explanations via explain(). Topics span
    twelve areas including ANOVA, t-tests, non-parametric tests,
    correlation, regression, chi-square, probability, and more.
